"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel's military has launched new strikes and destroyed a military command bunker. Huge traffic jams have formed after warnings for people to leave the Hezbollah stronghold, as Israel increases its strikes across Lebanon.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel Strikes Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de Israel ha hecho nuevos ataques y destruy\u00f3 un b\u00fanker de comando militar. Hay mucho tr\u00e1fico porque la gente tiene que salir de la zona de Hezbollah, ya que Israel aumenta sus ataques en L\u00edbano.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Israel Ataca L\u00edbano\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"China is not directly affected by the war in the Middle East yet, but it is feeling the indirect effects.\",            \"english_title\": \"China Feels War Effects\",            \"translated_version\": \"China no est\u00e1 afectada directamente por la guerra en el Medio Oriente todav\u00eda, pero siente los efectos indirectos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"China Siente Efectos de Guerra\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Kyiv is upset after Budapest officials accused staff transporting cash to Ukraine of money laundering. Ukraine's president says Kyiv will only help if it does not weaken its own air defenses.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kyiv Upset with Budapest\",            \"translated_version\": \"Kyiv est\u00e1 molesta porque funcionarios de Budapest acusaron a personas de llevar dinero a Ucrania para lavado de dinero. El presidente de Ucrania dice que Kyiv solo ayudar\u00e1 si no debilita sus defensas a\u00e9reas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Kyiv Molesta con Budapest\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US and another country have agreed to work together to promote stability after the US took action against Maduro and his wife.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Promotes Stability\",            \"translated_version\": \"Estados Unidos y otro pa\u00eds acordaron trabajar juntos para promover estabilidad despu\u00e9s de que Estados Unidos tom\u00f3 medidas contra Maduro y su esposa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"EEUU Promueve Estabilidad\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A country has limited young people's access to digital spaces to protect them from abuse.\",            \"english_title\": \"Digital Access Limited\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un pa\u00eds ha limitado el acceso de los j\u00f3venes a espacios digitales para protegerlos del abuso.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acceso Digital Limitado\"        }    ]}"